high_descs: Turn right and walk to the table on the left against the wall.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn around and walk forward to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Walk to the small side table to the left of the sink.
Put the knife on the side table, in front of and to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned knife on a side table.

high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the stove
Pick up a knife from the table
Move to the sink behind you
Clean the knife in the sink
Move to the left of the sink to the end table
Place the knife on the end table
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned knife on the black end table.

high_descs: Turn right, then turn left to face table.
Pick up knife from behind the potato and next to the pear.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put knife into sink next to green sponge, turn on water, turn off and drain water.
Pick up knife.  Turn around and go to small table with apple and pear on it, next to counter
Place the knife on the table, on top of the spoon, parallel to the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Washing a moving a knife to a table.
